{
  "texts": [
    "In addition to the MC metric, other cost-related metrics were also relatively underutilised.",
    "Specifically, the CWA metric was identified in only one paper, while cost curves and the weighted Kappa score were not employed.",
    "This finding highlights the need for increased emphasis on incorporating and exploring cost-related metrics in CSL research.",
    "It is also noteworthy that the vast majority of the selected studies incorporated several metrics in their performance evaluation.",
    "Combining multiple evaluation metrics is a widely adopted practice in ML research, particularly when dealing with imbalanced datasets."
  ]
}